{ 6...Qe8  7.c4  Qh5  @@StartBracket@@  7...d6  8.d4  transposes to the mainline.@@EndBracket@@ @@StartFEN@@rnb2rk1/ppppb1pp/4pn2/5p1q/2P5/1P3NP1/PB1PPPBP/RN1Q1RK1 w - - 1 8@@EndFEN@@  8.d4  d6  9.Nc3  transposes to the mainline.   6...Nc6  the knight doesn't belong on c6.  7.c4  d6  8.d4±  The plan: Nc3, d5, Rc1. }
7. d4 Qe8 8. c4 Qh5 9. Nc3 Nbd7
