{ Ruins Black's pawn structure @@StartBracket@@unless they want to play down a pawn@@EndBracket@@. }
13... gxf6
{ 13...Rxf6  14.Qd5+  wins a pawn.  14...Kh8  15.Nxe5+-   13...Nxf6  14.Nxe5+- }
