8. d4 { Aiming for Maroczy bind. } 8... cxd4
{ 8...Ne4  9.e3  transposes to @@StartFEN@@rnbqkbnr/pppppppp/8/8/8/8/PPPPPPPP/RNBQKBNR w KQkq - 0 1@@EndFEN@@  1.Nf3  Nf6  2.b3  g6  3.Bb2  Bg7  4.g3  O-O  5.Bg2  d6  6.d4  c5  7.c4  Ne4  8.O-O  Nc6  9.e3  @@StartBracket@@see the variation@@EndBracket@@. }
