13. Kxg2 Qa5 14. Rac1 a6 15. a4
{ As usual, stopping b5 forever. Black's rooks are suffocating, lacking the open files. }
15... Rac8 16. e4
{ As seen in the game Svidler,P @@StartBracket@@2765@@EndBracket@@ -Kokarev, D @@StartBracket@@2615@@EndBracket@@, Riadh 2017. Maroczy bind at its best. White stops any major pawn breaks like b5 or d5, and Black is suffocating without the open files and the lack of space. Plan: Rfe1, Re2, Rce1, Nd5 --> if Black takes on d5, take with the e-pawn and attack the weak Black's pawn on e7. }
