{ The position plays itself: just go h5 and mate on the h-file. Doesn't work  11...Nf6?  because of  12.Qxd8  Rxd8  13.Rxd8+  Nxd8  14.Nxe5+  The attack didn't go as planned but we can't really complain about being up a pawn. }
