1. Nf3 Nf6 2. b3 c5 3. Bb2 g6
{ A goofy move, basically saying 'hey, take on f6, we don't care'. Well, we will. }
4. Bxf6 exf6 5. c4 Bg7 6. Nc3
{ The plan: g3, Bg2, Rc1, O-O, d4. If you get this, remember to savor this position as much as you can and not rush. We can't guarantee such an exceptionally favorable start of the game will happen anytime soon. }
