{ 3...Nd7  4.d3  Ngf6  5.Nbd2  e6  6.g3  Be7  7.Bg2  O-O  8.O-O  transposes to @@StartFEN@@rn1qkbnr/ppp1pppp/8/3p1b2/8/1P3N2/PBPPPPPP/RN1QKB1R b KQkq - 2 3@@EndFEN@@  3...e6  4.g3  Nf6  5.Bg2  Be7  6.O-O  O-O  7.d3  Nbd7  8.Nbd2  @@StartBracket@@see the variation@@EndBracket@@.   3...f6  makes no sense because of  4.d4  and the pawn on f6 turns out to be punishing its own friendly knight on g8 while contributing nothing to the game. }
