{ 8...Nbd7  9.c4  c6  10.a3  a5  11.Qc2  transposes to the mainline.   8...c6  9.c4  Nbd7  10.a3  a5  11.Qc2  Bh7  12.Ne5  also transposes to the mainline.   8...a5  9.a3  a4?!  The following game is Yaro's win at the World Cup 2021. As you can see, we truly believe in what we recommend and employ all those lines ourselves! The whole game follows: 1-0 @@StartBracket@@38@@EndBracket@@ Zherebukh,Y @@StartBracket@@2620@@EndBracket@@-Ioannidis, E @@StartBracket@@2422@@EndBracket@@ Krasnaya Polyana 2021. }
9. c4 c6 10. a3 a5 11. Qc2 { The idea is to go Bc3 and then Qb2. } 11... Nbd7
12. Ne5 Nxe5
{ 12...Re8  13.Nxd7  Nxd7  14.Bc3  The plan: b4, Qb2, and attack on the queenside.   12...Rc8  13.Nxd7  Nxd7  14.b4!⩲  works out for the same reasons as in the 12... Bd6 line. }
