4. Bb2 a6 5. d4 cxd4 6. Nxd4 Nf6 7. Nxc6
{ The pawn structure a2-b3-c4-e3 vs. a6-c6-d5-e7 is typically better for White. }
7... bxc6 8. Nd2 g6
{ Looks a bit better for Black than e6 and the bishop on e7. } 9. Be2 Bg7 10.
O-O O-O 11. c4 a5 12. Rc1
