7... Be7 8. Bd3
{ The bishop is done on b5, and it's time to move on to the new exciting projects. }
8... O-O 9. a3 Ne4 10. c4
{ We need to gain space. The idea is to play Nc3, take on d5, and force the knight on e4 to leave or to trade for our knight on c3. }
10... cxd4 11. exd4 f5 { 11...Bf6  12.Qc2± } 12. Nc3 Rc8 13. cxd5
{ Forcing the trade on c3 and finally getting rid of the knight on e4. } 13...
Nxc3 14. Bxc3 exd5 15. Re1 { The plan: Qd2, b4, b5. Occupy the e5 square. } *

