e5 { Leads to a terrible pawn structure for Black. } 12. Bd5+
{ Pushing the king to h8 and making it harder for Black to move it towards the center in the endgame. }
12... Kh8 13. Bxc6 bxc6 14. dxe5 dxe5 15. Qxd8
{ Always trade queens if your pawn structure is significantly better. } 15...
Rxd8 16. Nd3 Re8 17. f4
