{ A mandatory capture, aiming to push the e-pawn and opening up the file. }
13... exf4 14. e5 Ng4 15. e6
{ An incredibly deep and strong pawn sacrifice. White is much better due to a total control of the e-file and almost all Black's pieces on the back rank. }
15... Bxe6 16. Rae1 { White's threats are overwhelming: Ba3, Ne4, h3. } *

